WEBVTT

00:11.000 --> 00:12.800
PREVIOUSLY ON THE L WORD...

00:12.833 --> 00:14.567
THIS IS MY CELL.

00:14.600 --> 00:15.733
CALL ME ANY TIME.

00:17.767 --> 00:19.367
