00:22.633 --> 00:24.567
THIS CHANGE OF LIFE IS REALLY--

00:24.600 --> 00:25.567
IT'S BEAUTIFUL,

00:25.600 --> 00:26.667
AND IT'S SEXY,
AND...

00:26.700 --> 00:28.800
THAT'S WHY I BROUGHT THE GUITAR.

00:28.833 --> 00:30.300
I'M NOT FISH OR FOWL.

00:30.333 --> 00:32.633
I WANT YOU
TO GET DRESSED, MAX.

00:32.667 --> 00:34.133
I WANT YOU TO WEAR
TIGHT TROUSERS.

00:35.833 --> 00:37.333
YOU LOOK REALLY HOT.

00:38.833 --> 00:40.500
