YOU COULD HOLD

01:44.633 --> 01:46.133
THAT EXPERIENCE
IN YOUR HAND.

01:51.300 --> 01:52.567
ARE YOU HARD?

01:52.600 --> 01:54.067
UM...

01:55.333 --> 01:57.533
[LAUGHS]

02:39.133 --> 02:42.067
ARE YOU OKAY?

02:42.067 --> 02:46.067
YOU'RE FUCKING THAT GUY
IN THE PHOTOGRAPH.

02:55.933 --> 02:59.600
