05:00.933 --> 05:04.133
WHOEVER IT IS THAT
YOU HAVE THESE FEELINGS FOR.

05:09.067 --> 05:11.367
NO.

05:11.400 --> 05:12.733
I HAVEN'T SLEPT WITH ANYONE.

05:12.767 --> 05:16.100
SO HE'S JUST THIS
AMORPHOUS MALE FIGURE

05:16.133 --> 05:17.867
COMPRISED ENTIRELY
OF CYBER POLLEN?

05:17.900 --> 05:21.800
THAT WAS A ONE-TIME THING
IN A CHAT ROOM.

05:21.833 --> 05:23.067
I THOUGHT
IT WAS JUST CURIOSITY.

05:23.100 --> 05:24.533
I THOUGHT
IT WOULD GO AWAY.

05:24.567 --> 05:27.200
BUT IT DIDN'T
GO AWAY.

05:27.233 --> 05:29.233
NO, IT DIDN'T.

05:34.667 --> 05:37.733
SO DADDYOF2 WAS JUST A...

05:37.767 --> 05:40.633
A TRANSITIONAL OBJECT?

05:40.667 --> 05:43.367
YEAH, I GUESS.

05:44.667 --> 05:45.633
[EXHALES]

05:45.667 --> 05:46.800
SO, UM...

05:51.433 --> 05:55.067
IS THERE A...

05:55.067 --> 06:00.067
IS THERE A REAL MAN
IN THE REAL WORLD SOMEWHERE?

06:00.067 --> 06:02.367
NO, I--

06:02.400 --> 06:03.600
I DON'T KNOW.

06:06.167 --> 06:07.433
OKAY, YEAH.

06:07.467 --> 06:09.433
I THINK SO.

06:12.400 --> 06:13.433
WHO IS IT?

06:13.467 --> 06:15.933
HIS NAME IS JOSH.

06:23.733 --> 06:25.533
THAT'S THE PRODUCER, RIGHT?

06:28.700 --> 06:29.867
RIGHT?

06:29.900 --> 06:31.333
NOTHING'S HAPPENED.

06:31.367 --> 06:33.633
FOR ALL I KNOW,
HE'S NOT EVEN INTERESTED IN ME.

06:33.667 --> 06:35.633
OH, TINA, PLEASE, OF COURSE
HE'S INTERESTED IN YOU.

06:37.067 --> 06:38.067
I'VE HEARD YOU
TALKING TO HIM

06:38.067 --> 06:39.100
ON THE PHONE.

06:39.133 --> 06:40.400
YOU CAN'T FLIRT LIKE THAT

06:40.433 --> 06:41.700
UNLESS SOMEONE
IS FLIRTING BACK WITH YOU.

07:02.667 --> 07:04.900
[ANGUS]: I LOVE YOU.

07:12.333 --> 07:15.800
YOU KNOW HOW MANY MEN
HAVE SAID THAT

07:15.833 --> 07:19.767
RIGHT AFTER THEY DID
WHAT YOU JUST DID?

07:21.767 --> 07:24.467
WELL, THAT'S
NONE OF MY BUSINESS.

07:24.500 --> 07:25.800
THEN...

07:25.833 --> 07:29.567
THEY SAY THEY'RE GOING
TO GO OUT FOR COFFEE,

07:29.600 --> 07:30.767
OR PUT GAS IN THE CAR,

07:30.800 --> 07:34.533
AND THEN
THREE YEARS LATER,

07:34.567 --> 07:37.067
I BUMP INTO THEM
IN THE STREET...

07:37.067 --> 07:38.767
ON A DAY
THAT I LOOK LIKE SHIT.

07:38.800 --> 07:42.067
WELL, I AM DIFFERENT.

07:42.067 --> 07:43.600
YOU'RE NOT
OLD ENOUGH TO KNOW

07:43.633 --> 07:47.367
THAT YOU ARE NO DIFFERENT
THAN ANY OTHER MAN.

07:47.400 --> 07:49.067
I AM 35 YEARS OLD--
OH, OH...

07:49.067 --> 07:51.067
I AM ALMOST
MIDDLE-AGED.

07:51.067 --> 07:52.833
NOW, THAT IS
CERTAINLY OLD ENOUGH

07:52.867 --> 07:56.867
TO KNOW
THAT I LOVE YOU.

07:56.900 --> 07:58.633
THAT'S A BIG WORD
YOU'RE THROWING AROUND.

07:58.667 --> 08:01.933
BIG.

08:01.967 --> 08:04.367
OKAY, IF YOU DON'T FEEL
THE SAME WAY,

08:04.400 --> 08:05.500
YOU DON'T FEEL THE SAME WAY.

08:05.533 --> 08:07.700
OH, ANGUS--

08:07.733 --> 08:09.600
NO, KIT, I KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE GOING TO SAY.

08:09.633 --> 08:11.633
YOU'RE GOING TO SAY,
"OH, LET'S TAKE MORE TIME,"

08:11.667 --> 08:13.900
AND THAT'S FINE.

08:13.933 --> 08:16.233
I MEAN, WE'VE GOT
ALL THE TIME IN THE WORLD,

08:16.267 --> 08:18.067
BUT THE ONE
THING I KNOW

08:18.067 --> 08:22.633
IS HOW I FEEL, AND...

08:22.667 --> 08:25.400
I DOUBT YOU DON'T
FEEL IT, TOO,

08:25.433 --> 08:27.133
BECAUSE, YOU KNOW,
I WAS THERE.

08:27.167 --> 08:28.433
[SIGHS]

08:28.467 --> 08:30.700
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
YOU WERE THERE, ANGUS?

08:30.733 --> 08:32.300
[STAMMERING]

08:32.333 --> 08:34.100
OKAY, SO WE HAD

08:34.133 --> 08:36.400
A COUPLE OF GOOD
ROLLS IN THE BARN.

08:36.433 --> 08:38.367
I COUNTED FOUR,
ACTUALLY.

08:38.400 --> 08:45.100
OKAY, OKAY,
FOUR FANTASTIC ORGASMS.

08:45.133 --> 08:48.533
OKAY, THANK YOU.
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

08:48.567 --> 08:50.700
[SIGHS]

08:50.733 --> 08:55.333
SO, WHAT, I'M JUST
YOUR BOY TOY?

08:55.367 --> 08:56.967
IS THAT IT?

08:57.067 --> 08:58.633
WELL, W--

08:58.667 --> 09:01.233
WOULD THAT BE BAD?

09:01.267 --> 09:03.633
YEAH, THAT'D BE BAD.

09:07.933 --> 09:11.067
I'M DEFINITELY NOT THAT GUY.

09:14.800 --> 09:17.167
