09:23.067 --> 09:24.367
HI, ALICE.

09:24.400 --> 09:27.100
HELLO, JANICE.

09:34.100 --> 09:35.200
OH, MY GOD,
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

09:35.233 --> 09:36.933
I DON'T KNOW,

09:36.967 --> 09:38.667
BUT I THINK I MAY HAVE
JUST BEEN RELEASED

09:38.700 --> 09:41.500
FROM MY MORTAL COILS.

09:43.067 --> 09:46.933
HEY, JANICE...

09:46.967 --> 09:49.200
WOULD YOU MIND...

09:49.233 --> 09:52.400
DISPOSING OF THIS
OBSOLETE THING?

09:52.433 --> 09:53.867
TRASH OR RECYCLING?

09:53.900 --> 09:55.067
TRASH, RECYCLING.
I DON'T KNOW.

09:55.067 --> 09:56.800
CAN YOU RECYCLE
FOAM CORE?

09:56.833 --> 09:58.233
I DON'T KNOW.

09:58.267 --> 09:59.900
YEAH, WELL,
I DON'T GIVE A FUCK,

10:00.067 --> 10:02.900
BECAUSE I AM FREE AT LAST.

10:02.933 --> 10:04.000
WHOO!

10:09.733 --> 10:10.933
OH, HERE, BABY,
LET ME GET IT.

10:23.333 --> 10:25.000
YOU KNOW,
I DON'T NEED DEODORANT.

10:25.033 --> 10:27.400
