YOU CAN HANDLE IT, OKAY?

14:16.900 --> 14:18.633
YES, SEE, WE'RE NOT EVEN
THAT BUSY, OKAY?

14:18.667 --> 14:19.600
WE'RE SLAMMED.

14:19.633 --> 14:20.667
THAT'S OKAY.

14:20.700 --> 14:23.500
[BILLIE]:
JESUS...

14:23.533 --> 14:25.467
I'M SORRY,
SO NOT TO BE ANAL,

14:25.500 --> 14:28.533
BUT HOW MUCH OF THE CONTENT
WOULD I HAVE TO CHANGE?

14:28.567 --> 14:30.200
NOT ALL
THAT MUCH.

14:30.233 --> 14:31.767
I'M GIVING YOU
ONE OF OUR MOST GIFTED EDITORS,

14:31.800 --> 14:33.433
NEVE SARAFIAN.

14:33.467 --> 14:34.967
OH, MY GOD, WOW.

14:35.067 --> 14:36.867
JENNY, YOU'VE WRITTEN
A WONDERFUL BOOK,

14:36.900 --> 14:39.267
AND I REALLY WANT
TO GET IT OUT THERE.

14:40.667 --> 14:43.433
HERE YOU GO.

14:43.467 --> 14:45.067
WHAT IS THIS?

14:45.067 --> 14:47.333
THE FIRST HALF OF YOUR ADVANCE.

14:47.367 --> 14:49.333
TAKE A LOOK.

14:58.067 --> 15:00.633
WILL YOU EXCUSE ME
JUST FOR ONE SECOND?

15:00.667 --> 15:01.433
JUST...

15:01.467 --> 15:02.833
OF COURSE.

15:05.500 --> 15:07.767
OH, MY GOD! OH, MY GOD!
OH, MY GOD! OH, MY GOD!

15:07.800 --> 15:08.867
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT!

15:08.900 --> 15:10.067
[SQUEALING]

15:10.067 --> 15:11.133
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT!

15:11.167 --> 15:12.900
OH, MY GOD, I'M SO HAPPY!

15:14.967 --> 15:16.867
MAYBE WE SHOULD TAKE
THAT TRIP TO PARIS

15:16.900 --> 15:17.867
