15:25.867 --> 15:27.200
CAN SHE COME WITH ME?

15:27.233 --> 15:28.200
OF COURSE.

15:28.233 --> 15:29.467
OKAY.

15:31.267 --> 15:32.933
OKAY, IF YOU'LL PUT THIS ON...

15:32.967 --> 15:35.333
SOMEBODY WILL BE WITH YOU
IN A MOMENT.

15:37.333 --> 15:38.633
THANKS.

15:38.667 --> 15:39.800
AND WE DO LIKE
OUR PATIENTS

15:39.833 --> 15:42.067
