15:48.900 --> 15:51.233
OKAY?
OKAY.

16:38.267 --> 16:40.700
ARE YOU IN LOVE WITH HER?

16:42.067 --> 16:44.333
NO.

16:46.300 --> 16:47.800
ARE YOU SURE?

16:49.167 --> 16:51.133
YEAH.

16:56.233 --> 16:58.567
PLEASE, CARMEN, I DON'T WANT
TO MAKE THIS INTO A BIG DEAL.

16:58.600 --> 17:00.200
YOU GO ALL THE WAY
OVER TO SOMEBODY'S BEACH HOUSE,

17:00.233 --> 17:01.333
AND YOU FUCK THEM
TILL THE SUN COMES UP,

17:01.367 --> 17:02.367
