MUCH MORE PROGRESSED

32:14.700 --> 32:17.833
THAN WE ANTICIPATED.

32:17.867 --> 32:20.400
THE CANCER HAS METASTASIZED
TO THE LYMPH NODES.

32:20.433 --> 32:22.533
WE HAD TO REMOVE

32:22.567 --> 32:24.233
A GREAT DEAL
OF MUSCLE AND TISSUE.

32:26.767 --> 32:29.067
HI, UTA, UM, IT'S ALICE.

32:29.067 --> 32:30.533
I, UM--

32:30.567 --> 32:32.267
SOMETHING'S HAPPENED,

32:32.300 --> 32:34.733
AND I'M GOING TO HAVE
TO CANCEL TONIGHT, BUT, UM...

32:34.767 --> 32:37.067
I JUST-- I CAN'T REALLY
TALK ABOUT IT RIGHT NOW,

32:37.100 --> 32:40.933
BUT I'M REALLY SORRY.

32:40.967 --> 32:42.233
OKAY.

32:42.267 --> 32:43.333
I'LL TALK TO YOU LATER.

32:54.367 --> 32:58.067
I THOUGHT YOU PUT ME IN CHARGE.

32:59.467 --> 33:01.467
UM, SORRY, TINA.

33:01.500 --> 33:03.067
WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

33:03.067 --> 33:04.767
YOU TOLD ME
YOU WOULD FOLLOW MY LEAD

33:04.800 --> 33:06.567
AND LET ME RUN THE COMPANY.

33:06.600 --> 33:09.133
I CAN'T HAVE YOU UNDERMINE ME
IN A MEETING LIKE THAT.

33:10.833 --> 33:12.300
SORRY.

33:12.333 --> 33:14.667
IT WON'T HAPPEN AGAIN.

33:17.400 --> 33:20.067
OKAY.

33:20.067 --> 33:21.767
THANKS.

33:21.800 --> 33:22.867
TINA...

33:24.500 --> 33:25.967
CAN I ASK YOU A QUESTION?

33:26.067 --> 33:27.567
SURE.

33:29.667 --> 33:30.900
HAVE YOU EVER...

33:32.867 --> 33:34.900
FALLEN IN LOVE
WITH A STRAIGHT WOMAN?

33:34.933 --> 33:37.067
OH, GOD...

33:37.067 --> 33:39.700
HELENA, YOU'RE ASKING
THE WRONG PERSON.

33:39.733 --> 33:42.233
I WAS STRAIGHT
UNTIL I MET BETTE.

33:42.267 --> 33:46.100
WELL, THEN, TALK TO ME
AS A STRAIGHT WOMAN.

33:46.133 --> 33:47.300
WHAT WENT THROUGH YOUR MIND

33:47.333 --> 33:48.433
WHEN YOU FIRST HAD
THOSE FEELINGS?

33:48.467 --> 33:49.967
IT WAS TERRIFYING.

33:50.067 --> 33:52.733
I MEAN, THE FALLING IN LOVE PART
FEELS GOOD,

33:52.767 --> 33:54.633
BUT THERE'S SO MUCH
TO WRAP YOUR HEAD AROUND.

33:54.667 --> 33:55.733
BUT WHY?

33:55.767 --> 33:58.767
I MEAN, ISN'T LOVE JUST LOVE?

33:58.800 --> 34:00.633
NO, IT ISN'T.

34:00.667 --> 34:04.067
IT'S NOT THE LIFE
THAT MOST STRAIGHT WOMEN WANT.

34:04.100 --> 34:06.933
MOST OF US--

34:06.967 --> 34:08.500
MOST STRAIGHT WOMEN--

34:08.533 --> 34:09.767
THEY SPEND SO MUCH TIME

34:09.800 --> 34:11.467
PREPARING
FOR THE HUSBAND,

34:11.500 --> 34:13.267
THE KIDS,
THE HOUSE...

34:13.300 --> 34:16.867
IT'S TOO MUCH TO UNDO.

34:16.900 --> 34:19.067
I JUST DON'T
UNDERSTAND, YOU KNOW.

34:19.067 --> 34:23.533
HOW CAN SOMEONE BE SO THERE,

34:23.567 --> 34:24.533
AND THEN--

34:24.567 --> 34:25.867
HELENA...

34:27.067 --> 34:28.567
CAN I GIVE YOU SOME ADVICE?

34:30.067 --> 34:31.067
PLEASE.

34:31.067 --> 34:33.133
JUST LET IT GO.

34:33.167 --> 34:35.367
IT ALMOST NEVER TURNS OUT
LIKE YOU WANT IT TO.

34:35.400 --> 34:37.400
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

34:40.800 --> 34:42.067
OH, I'M SORRY.

34:44.667 --> 34:48.233
UM, COULD I--
COULD I TALK TO YOU?

34:49.400 --> 34:50.367
OF COURSE.

34:50.400 --> 34:52.633
I SHOULD GO

34:52.667 --> 34:54.267
IF I'M GOING TO MAKE
THAT SCREENING.

34:54.300 --> 34:55.300
I REALLY SHOULD.

35:02.967 --> 35:04.067
WHAT--

36:47.133 --> 36:48.967
I'M SO GLAD
YOU'RE HERE.

37:00.833 --> 37:02.833
IRWIN, SHARON, HI.

37:02.867 --> 37:06.067
ALICE, WHAT ARE
YOU DOING HERE?

37:06.067 --> 37:07.133
WELL, WE'D REALLY
LIKE TO KNOW

37:07.167 --> 37:08.400
WHAT'S GOING ON
WITH DANA.

37:08.433 --> 37:10.300
NO ONE'S TELLING US, AND...

37:10.333 --> 37:11.767
THEY REMOVED
HER BREAST,

37:11.800 --> 37:13.067
AND FOUND IT'S
ALREADY SPREAD.

37:15.267 --> 37:18.567
OH, MY GOD.

37:18.600 --> 37:20.200
YOU SHOULD BOTH
GO HOME NOW.

37:20.233 --> 37:21.233
THERE'S NOTHING
EITHER OF YOU CAN DO

37:21.267 --> 37:24.400
RIGHT HERE.

37:27.067 --> 37:29.900
WELL, I'M SURE...

37:29.933 --> 37:32.300
I'M SURE DANA WOULD WANT
LARA TO BE IN THERE--

37:32.333 --> 37:34.667
ALICE, DANA
IS VERY SICK,

37:34.700 --> 37:37.067
AND SHE NEEDS
HER REST.

37:40.767 --> 37:42.333
LISTEN...

37:42.367 --> 37:43.967
I CAN'T EVEN BEGIN TO IMAGINE

37:44.067 --> 37:46.600
WHAT YOU'RE GOING THROUGH
RIGHT NOW,

37:46.633 --> 37:50.067
BUT LARA'S DANA'S PARTNER.

37:50.100 --> 37:53.967
WE REALLY NEED
TO RESPECT THAT.

37:54.067 --> 37:55.400
SHE LOVES YOUR DAUGHTER
VERY MUCH.

37:55.433 --> 37:58.233
DANA NEEDS HER RIGHT NOW,
I'M SORRY.

38:08.067 --> 38:10.300
HEY...

38:10.333 --> 38:11.300
HEY, YOU.

38:11.333 --> 38:12.300
WHERE'D YOU GO?

38:12.333 --> 38:15.800
I'M RIGHT
HERE, BABY.

38:15.833 --> 38:19.300
ALICE IS HERE, TOO.

38:19.333 --> 38:21.733
SHE IS?

38:21.767 --> 38:22.800
WHERE IS SHE?

38:26.867 --> 38:28.133
I'M RIGHT HERE.

38:38.667 --> 38:39.700
COME HERE.

38:54.067 --> 38:55.067
DO YOU NEED
ANY HELP?

38:55.100 --> 38:57.200
NO, I'VE GOT IT, THANKS.

39:10.433 --> 39:13.067
SO DID ANYTHING
HAPPEN TODAY?

39:13.067 --> 39:14.633
I HAD THIS RUN-IN
WITH HELENA,

39:14.667 --> 39:15.767
AND YOU'D BE
PROUD OF ME.

39:15.800 --> 39:17.167
I STOOD
RIGHT UP TO HER.

39:17.200 --> 39:18.900
I WASN'T REALLY
TALKING ABOUT THAT.

39:18.933 --> 39:21.933
BETTE, DON'T GO THERE.

39:21.967 --> 39:24.667
JOSH IS THIS PRODUCER
I WORK WITH ON A PROJECT.

39:24.700 --> 39:26.067
I TALK TO HIM
ONCE A WEEK,

39:26.067 --> 39:27.167
AND WHEN I DO,

39:27.200 --> 39:28.533
I TALK TO HIM
ABOUT BUSINESS.

39:28.567 --> 39:30.067
WELL, I JUST THOUGHT
MAYBE IT'S HORMONAL,

39:30.100 --> 39:31.233
THIS THING
THAT YOU'RE GOING THROUGH.

39:31.267 --> 39:35.133
I ONLY DATED MEN
BEFORE I MET YOU.

39:35.167 --> 39:36.533
SO WHAT WAS I,

39:36.567 --> 39:37.633
SOME EIGHT-AND-A-HALF-YEAR
ABERRATION?

39:44.300 --> 39:45.900
HELLO?

39:47.600 --> 39:49.367
HI...

39:49.400 --> 39:50.467
HEY, CAN YOU
GIVE ME A HAND WITH THIS?

39:50.500 --> 39:51.933
MM-HMM.

39:51.967 --> 39:54.300
THANKS.

39:54.333 --> 39:55.367
HEY, KIT.

39:55.400 --> 39:56.633
HEY.

39:56.667 --> 39:57.800
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING--

39:57.833 --> 39:59.867
OH, MY FUCKING GOD.

39:59.900 --> 40:01.733
YOU'VE GOT TO BE KIDDING ME.

40:01.767 --> 40:03.467
OKAY,
WHERE'S ANGELICA?

40:03.500 --> 40:04.533
NAPPING.

40:08.433 --> 40:09.567
OKAY, THIS IS
JUST UNBELIEVABLE,

40:09.600 --> 40:10.633
AND I CAN'T EVEN
BELIEVE

40:10.667 --> 40:13.267
THAT I EVEN
HAVE TO SAY THIS,

40:13.300 --> 40:14.567
BUT OF ALL THE MEN
IN LOS ANGELES,

40:14.600 --> 40:15.533
CUTE LITTLE BONY ASS OR NOT,

40:15.567 --> 40:16.633
YOU HAVE TO GO AFTER

40:16.667 --> 40:19.100
THE ONE GUY
IN OUR DAUGHTER'S LIFE?

40:19.133 --> 40:21.000
SHE'S SOUND ASLEEP.

40:21.033 --> 40:22.400
SHE DIDN'T
GO AFTER ME,

40:22.433 --> 40:23.967
I WENT AFTER HER.

40:24.000 --> 40:26.133
I'VE BEEN FUCKING
RELENTLESS.

40:26.167 --> 40:27.533
I NEVER FELL
THIS HARD FOR A WOMAN

40:27.567 --> 40:28.633
IN MY ENTIRE LIFE.

40:28.667 --> 40:32.300
WOW.

40:32.333 --> 40:33.300
ALL RIGHT, WELL,

40:33.333 --> 40:34.367
WHAT ABOUT
WHEN YOU BREAK UP?

40:34.400 --> 40:35.033
WE'RE NOT GOING
TO BREAK UP.

40:35.067 --> 40:36.400
NO?

40:36.433 --> 40:38.200
ANGUS, YOU DON'T KNOW
ABOUT THAT.

40:38.233 --> 40:39.800
WE'RE-- WE'RE JUST--

40:39.833 --> 40:40.800
YOU'RE JUST WHAT?

40:42.167 --> 40:43.533
DATING?

40:43.567 --> 40:44.867
AND MAKING OUT

40:44.900 --> 40:47.067
LIKE A COUPLE OF TEENAGERS,

40:47.100 --> 40:48.633
WHICH I THINK
IS GREAT.

40:48.667 --> 40:51.133
IT'S GREAT, AS LONG
AS YOU STILL BABY-SIT, OKAY?

40:51.167 --> 40:53.267
CONGRATULATIONS.

40:53.300 --> 40:54.533
OH, GREAT.

40:54.567 --> 40:56.100
OKAY, HUG, HUG,
THAT'S FANTASTIC.

40:56.133 --> 40:57.367
BUT WE NEED SOME RULES.

40:57.400 --> 40:59.033
RULES?

40:59.067 --> 41:00.533
YEAH, LIKE,
NO SEX IN FRONT OF THE BABY.

41:00.567 --> 41:02.067
OF COURSE NOT.

41:02.067 --> 41:04.267
KIT?

41:04.300 --> 41:05.933
NO SEX
IN FRONT OF THE BABY.

41:05.967 --> 41:07.267
NO SEX IN OUR BED.

41:12.067 --> 41:14.867
UGH...

41:14.900 --> 41:18.267
WILL YOU GO
CHANGE THE SHEETS, PLEASE?

41:20.733 --> 41:22.433
[***]

41:27.567 --> 41:29.633
HELLO! HELLO!

41:29.667 --> 41:30.833
HOW YOU DOING?

41:30.867 --> 41:32.067
CONGRATULATIONS!

41:32.100 --> 41:33.533
HEY.

41:33.567 --> 41:34.567
I'M SO PROUD OF YOU.

41:34.600 --> 41:35.767
YOU ARE?

41:35.800 --> 41:37.067
I'M FINALLY FUCKING
HAVE MONEY!

41:37.067 --> 41:39.067
YOU HAVE MONEY!
OH, MY GOSH.

41:40.167 --> 41:41.800
OH, FUCK, I'M SORRY.

41:41.833 --> 41:43.100
I'M DRUNK,
AND WE'RE CELEBRATING,

41:43.133 --> 41:45.067
SO PLEASE GET DRINKS.

41:45.100 --> 41:49.333
OKAY, YES, UM,
A BEER, HONEY, YES.

41:49.367 --> 41:50.900
MOIRA, THAT'S GOT
TO BE GREAT FOR YOU,

41:50.933 --> 41:53.367
TO HAVE A GIRLFRIEND
WITH SOME MONEY, RIGHT?

41:53.400 --> 41:55.933
YEAH,
I'M REALLY PROUD OF HER.

41:55.967 --> 41:57.833
I'LL BE MAKING MY OWN MONEY
SOON, SO...

41:57.867 --> 42:00.067
OF COURSE.
OF COURSE YOU WILL.

42:00.067 --> 42:01.067
WHAT UP, EVERYBODY!

42:01.067 --> 42:02.200
[CROWD CHEERS EXPLOSIVELY]

42:05.300 --> 42:07.800
I GOT SOMETHING SWEET
FOR YOU TONIGHT.

42:07.833 --> 42:09.100
ALL THE WAY
FROM PORTLAND, OREGON,

42:09.133 --> 42:10.200
WHERE THEY PLAY VIDEO POKER,

42:10.233 --> 42:12.067
BUT YOU DON'T HAVE
TO FEEL BAD ABOUT IT,

42:12.100 --> 42:15.400
BECAUSE ALL THE MONEY
GOES TO THE SCHOOL SYSTEM.

42:15.433 --> 42:17.933
THESE SISTERS
ARE BAD TO THE BONE.

42:17.967 --> 42:21.567
I WANT YOU TO GIVE IT UP
FOR SLEATER-KINNEY!

42:31.400 --> 42:35.067
[PERFORMING "JUMPERS"]

42:38.367 --> 42:41.767
* I SPEND THE AFTERNOON
IN CARS *

42:41.800 --> 42:45.367
* I SIT IN TRAFFIC JAMS
FOR HOURS *

42:45.400 --> 42:51.067
* DON'T PUSH ME
I AM NOT OKAY *

42:51.067 --> 42:54.667
* THE SKY IS BLUE
MOST EVERY DAY *

42:54.700 --> 42:58.067
* THE LEMONS GROW LIKE TUMORS

42:58.067 --> 43:02.967
* THEY ARE TINY SUNS
INFUSED WITH SOUR *

43:08.833 --> 43:11.967
* LONELY AS A CLOUD...

43:12.067 --> 43:14.900
HEY, MAX, I HEARD
YOU WANTED TO TALK ME.

43:14.933 --> 43:21.167
* IN THE GOLDEN STATE

43:21.200 --> 43:27.300
* THE COLDEST WINTER
THAT I EVER SAW *

43:27.333 --> 43:32.400
* WAS THE SUMMER THAT I SPENT

43:32.433 --> 43:34.367
SO, WHAT'S
ON YOUR MIND?

43:34.400 --> 43:36.500
I WANTED TO SEE IF I COULD
TAKE YOU UP ON THAT OFFER.

43:36.533 --> 43:38.067
TO TALK TO TOM.

43:38.100 --> 43:39.667
THINK IT WOULD BE COOL
IF I CALLED HIM?

43:39.700 --> 43:41.167
YEAH, SURE, MAX.

43:41.200 --> 43:42.300
YOU CAN CALL HIM ANY TIME.

43:42.333 --> 43:43.767
HERE'S HIS NUMBER.

43:43.800 --> 43:45.700
YOU WANT TO KNOW
HOW TO DO IT,

43:45.733 --> 43:47.067
DON'T YOU?

43:47.067 --> 43:48.767
YOU WANT THE DETAILS.

43:48.800 --> 43:50.567
YEAH.

43:50.600 --> 43:53.633
YOU WANT TO KNOW
HOW MAX CAN FULLY BECOME...

43:53.667 --> 43:54.733
MAX.

43:54.767 --> 43:56.667
THANKS.

43:59.500 --> 44:03.067
WOW.

44:03.067 --> 44:04.467
THAT'S A GOOD START, MAX.

44:20.833 --> 44:26.933
* THE COLDEST WINTER
THAT I EVER SAW *

44:26.967 --> 44:29.300
* WAS THE SUMMER
THAT I SPENT... *

44:29.333 --> 44:30.633
HAVE YOU SEEN MOIRA?

44:30.667 --> 44:31.833
NO.

44:31.867 --> 44:33.400
NO?

44:33.433 --> 44:35.133
I'LL BE BACK. I'M GOING
TO LOOK FOR HER.

45:02.933 --> 45:06.067
JENNY, UM...

45:06.100 --> 45:08.533
WE WERE JUST, UH...

45:08.567 --> 45:12.700
IS THIS THE KIND
OF RELATIONSHIP THAT YOU WANT?

45:14.133 --> 45:15.800
BECAUSE IF IT IS,
I DON'T--

45:15.833 --> 45:16.867
JENNY, MAX IS
CRAZY ABOUT--

45:16.900 --> 45:17.900
SHUT UP.

45:19.433 --> 45:20.400
LOOK--

45:22.667 --> 45:26.500
IT'S JUST-- HE MADE ME FEEL
LIKE A REAL GUY.

45:26.533 --> 45:29.233
YOU KNOW?

45:29.267 --> 45:30.567
I MEAN, IT WASN'T
JUST LIKE

45:30.600 --> 45:32.733
SOME GIRL
WITH THIS THING IN HER PANTS.

45:43.400 --> 45:45.533
OKAY.

45:49.200 --> 45:50.633
OKAY.

45:52.533 --> 45:54.900
IT'S OKAY.

46:00.667 --> 46:04.200
DON'T HIDE.

46:05.900 --> 46:06.900
OKAY.

46:06.933 --> 46:07.933
LET'S GO.

46:19.133 --> 46:23.833
* BE STILL THIS SAD DAY
BE STILL THIS SAD YEAR *

46:23.867 --> 46:26.467
* HOPE YOUR LAST HOPE
FEAR YOUR LAST FEAR *

46:26.500 --> 46:28.700
* YOU'RE NOT THE ONLY ONE
YOU'RE NOT THE ONLY ONE *

46:28.733 --> 46:32.667
* YOU'RE NOT THE ONLY ONE
YOU'RE NOT THE ONLY ONE *

46:32.700 --> 46:33.967
* LET'S GO!

46:34.067 --> 46:35.233
[CELLPHONE RINGING]

46:35.267 --> 46:36.333
ALICE, WHERE
THE FUCK ARE YOU?

46:36.367 --> 46:38.633
SLEATER-KINNEY'S AMAZING!

46:38.667 --> 46:40.100
WHAT? LISTEN.

46:41.967 --> 46:43.200
WHERE ARE YOU?

46:43.233 --> 46:44.933
WHAT?

47:05.367 --> 47:09.667
* MY FALLING SHAPE
WILL DRAW A LINE *

47:09.700 --> 47:12.833
* BETWEEN THE BLUE
OF SEA AND SKY *

47:12.867 --> 47:17.067
* I'M NOT A BIRD
I'M NOT A PLANE *

47:19.267 --> 47:22.567
* I TOOK A TAXI TO THE GATE

47:22.600 --> 47:25.867
* I WILL NOT
GO TO SCHOOL AGAIN *

47:25.900 --> 47:29.667
* FOUR SECONDS WAS
THE LONGEST WAIT *

47:32.100 --> 47:36.533
* FOUR SECONDS
WAS THE LONGEST WAIT-- **

47:53.067 --> 47:54.067
THERE SHE IS.

47:54.067 --> 47:55.767
ALICE...

47:58.600 --> 48:01.600
HEY, GUYS.

48:03.633 --> 48:06.733
HONEY, YOU MUST BE
SO EXHAUSTED.

48:06.767 --> 48:09.067
SHE'S REALLY SICK.

48:09.067 --> 48:10.567
WHAT HAPPENED?

48:10.600 --> 48:13.300
I THOUGHT IT WAS
A BENIGN LUMP.

48:13.333 --> 48:16.100
SHE DIDN'T TELL US THE TRUTH,

48:16.133 --> 48:18.833
AND IT'S A LOT WORSE
THAN THEY THOUGHT,

48:18.867 --> 48:20.900
AND THE CANCER
HAS SPREAD.

48:20.933 --> 48:22.300
OH, FUCK.

48:22.333 --> 48:25.067
FUCK.

48:26.833 --> 48:28.200
DO YOU GUYS WANT TO SEE HER?

48:28.233 --> 48:29.200
YEAH.

48:29.233 --> 48:31.233
OKAY, COME ON.

48:43.067 --> 48:44.833
HI.

48:54.067 --> 48:55.867
HEY, DANA.

49:03.667 --> 49:06.067
[WEAKLY]: HI.

49:08.333 --> 49:12.400
WHAT YOU DOING
IN HERE, BABY GIRL?

49:26.767 --> 49:29.133
[WHISPERING]: DANA...

49:29.167 --> 49:30.300
SWEETIE...

49:37.133 --> 49:39.700
WE LOVE YOU.

49:42.967 --> 49:44.133
DO YOU KNOW THAT?

49:44.167 --> 49:45.067
DO YOU KNOW WE LOVE YOU?

49:45.067 --> 49:47.167
YEAH.

49:47.200 --> 49:49.933
